{"result":true,"items":[{"_id":1692659174,"link":"https://www.instagram.com/reel/DSZlLLKAXeu/?igsh=MXVnZW1ienM1ZTcyYg==","excerpt":"11K likes, 62 comments - ethan_kuan_kuan on December 18, 2025: \"「這次我們要來把福岡最紅的明太子醬，打包7條通通帶回家！」\n-\n福岡最紅的就是明太子周邊，上次買了各式各樣的明太子麵包，在網友的推薦下，這次直接來專賣店買了大量的明太子醬，位於祇園站的1號出口「島本」明太子醬，在阪急百貨也有分店，一進來店員就給我們瘋狂試吃！\n-\n店員貼心附上中文說明，大條的1100元日幣，小條的500元日幣，另外可以購買保冷袋，12小時內回家快速冷藏，建議大家最後一天上飛機前再來買就好，店員被我們的大採購嚇到了！\n-\n順手還買了一罐柚子胡椒，想說回來配湯配飯應該都很開胃，跟店員說了再見後，就準備塞回行李箱一路帶回台灣，朋友們收到後都超級幸福的，如果有要來福岡玩的朋友，這條明太子醬很便宜，又可以讓你充滿幸福感！先把這集傳給你的好朋友吧！\n-\n📌島本博多站前店\n地址：〒812-0037 福岡縣福岡市博多區御供所町2-63.\n地鐵：福岡市地下鐵機場線祇園站下車1號出口\n時間：0900-1900\".","note":"","type":"image","user":{"$ref":"users","$id":6938240},"cover":"https://scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/591124760_739191171981959_6494394874113307133_n.jpg?stp=cmp1_dst-jpg_e35_s640x640_tt6&_nc_cat=104&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0xJUFMuYmVzdF9pbWFnZV91cmxnZW4uQzMifQ%3D%3D&_nc_ohc=I4DdQqRwu2IQ7kNvwHz3mNU&_nc_oc=Adp9Drlul_jWHzADXTK6ffkkbKNxKEbukxzN6bhWTHwRtaED9xnhKzlve_GedbHVALA&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_gid=i8oq5Qa379D1AH6osjpeqA&_nc_ss=7a289&oh=00_Af1xDK5oUhTGd5oj3z2MVJzojqy3K90SVWQzbjDKn3Rr-Q&oe=69EE27EC","media":[{"link":"https://scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/591124760_739191171981959_6494394874113307133_n.jpg?stp=cmp1_dst-jpg_e35_s640x640_tt6&_nc_cat=104&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0xJUFMuYmVzdF9pbWFnZV91cmxnZW4uQzMifQ%3D%3D&_nc_ohc=I4DdQqRwu2IQ7kNvwHz3mNU&_nc_oc=Adp9Drlul_jWHzADXTK6ffkkbKNxKEbukxzN6bhWTHwRtaED9xnhKzlve_GedbHVALA&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_gid=i8oq5Qa379D1AH6osjpeqA&_nc_ss=7a289&oh=00_Af1xDK5oUhTGd5oj3z2MVJzojqy3K90SVWQzbjDKn3Rr-Q&oe=69EE27EC","type":"image"}],"tags":["旅遊"],"removed":false,"collection":{"$ref":"collections","$id":70031060,"oid":70031060},"highlights":[],"created":"2026-04-22T06:23:12.761Z","lastUpdate":"2026-04-22T06:23:44.667Z","domain":"instagram.com","title":"福岡 - 明太子醬","creatorRef":{"_id":